## 3. AI 行为树系统

### 3.1 行为树框架

```
BTNode (abstract)
├── BTComposite
│   ├── BTSelector     子节点有一个成功就返回 Success
│   └── BTSequence     子节点全部成功才返回 Success
├── BTDecorator
│   ├── BTInverter     反转结果
│   ├── BTCooldown     冷却时间内返回 Failure
│   └── BTCondition    条件检查
└── BTAction
    ├── BTMoveTo       移动到目标
    ├── BTAttack       攻击目标
    ├── BTFlee         逃离目标（医疗兵专用）
    ├── BTWait         等待 N 秒
    └── BTEmitEvent    发布事件（治疗/呼叫支援等）
```

### 3.2 各单位行为树

**民兵（炮灰，直线冲）**
```
Selector
├── Sequence [射程内]
│   ├── Condition: NearestEnemyInRange
│   └── Action: Attack
├── Sequence [看见敌人]
│   ├── Condition: NearestEnemyInAggroRange
│   └── Action: MoveToward(NearestEnemy)
└── Action: Idle
```

**RPG 兵（远程溅射，保持距离）**
```
Selector
├── Sequence [太近了 → 后退]
│   ├── Condition: NearestEnemyDistance < 5
│   └── Action: MoveAway(NearestEnemy, desiredDistance=10)
├── Sequence [射程内 → 发射]
│   ├── Condition: NearestEnemyInRange
│   └── Action: Attack (优先攻击密集目标)
├── Sequence [看见 → 接近到射程]
│   └── Action: MoveToward(NearestEnemy)
└── Action: Idle
```

**武装皮卡（高速绕侧）**
```
Selector
├── Sequence [射程内且未受伤严重]
│   ├── Condition: NearestEnemyInRange && Health > 40%
│   └── Action: Attack (扫射)
├── Sequence [受伤严重 → 脱离]
│   ├── Condition: Health < 40%
│   └── Action: Flee(NearestEnemy)
├── Sequence [利用速度绕侧翼]
│   ├── Condition: CanFlank
│   └── Action: MoveToFlankPosition
└── Action: MoveToward(NearestEnemy)
```

**军阀 Boss（多阶段）**
```
Selector
├── Sequence [血量<25% → 狂暴]
│   ├── Condition: Health < 25%
│   ├── Action: SetSpeedMultiplier(1.5)
│   └── Action: Attack(rocket_barrage, cooldown × 0.5)
├── Sequence [血量<50% → 火箭弹幕模式]
│   ├── Condition: Health < 50%
│   └── Action: Attack(rocket_barrage)
├── Sequence [默认 → 重机枪扫射]
│   ├── Condition: NearestEnemyInRange
│   └── Action: Attack(heavy_mg)
└── Action: MoveToward(NearestEnemy)
```

**医疗兵（跟随 + 治疗）**
```
Selector
├── Sequence [周围友方受伤]
│   ├── Condition: NearbyAllyBelowHealth(70%)
│   └── Action: Heal(NearestInjuredAlly)
├── Sequence [自己被攻击 → 逃跑]
│   ├── Condition: IsBeingAttacked
│   └── Action: Flee(NearestEnemy)
└── Action: FollowFormation
```

